### Get profile (requires Better Auth token)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create collection
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/collections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "My Collection"
}

### Create problem
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/problems
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "collection_id": "{{collection_id}}",
  "original_image_url": "https://example.com/image.png"
}

### Trigger OCR
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/problems/{{problem_id}}/ocr
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "idempotency_key": "ocr-1"
}

### Export PDF
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/collections/{{collection_id}}/export_pdf
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "idempotency_key": "pdf-1"
}
